EasyXLS v8.6.0 API Specification

Namespaces 
Namespace Description
EasyXLS Provides the classes necessary to write/read a Microsoft Excel document.
EasyXLS.Charts Contains classes used for working with chart components.
EasyXLS.Constants Provides classes that contain constants used all over the library.
EasyXLS.Drawings Provides classes for working with drawings like shapes, images, textboxes, comments.
EasyXLS.Drawings.Formatting Provides classes used for formatting the drawings.
EasyXLS.FileProperties Contains classes used for setting the document properties.
EasyXLS.PivotTables Contains classes used for working with pivot tables.
EasyXLS.Themes Contains classes for setting the theme properties.
EasyXLS.Util Contains miscellaneous utility classes.
